snippet.title: [SSATZ] SuperStarATEEZ GRAND OPEN!
snippet.description:
멈춘 심장이 뛰는걸 보니 #SuperStarATEEZ 정식 오픈이렸다
보고만 있을텐가? 지금 내 손안에 #슈스티즈 가 있는데?
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The heart that stopped start to beating was a #SuperStarATEEZ official opening
You just gonna watch? I have a #SSATZ in my hand right now.
